title: SET_INSTANCE_PRIORITY_MODE

0x9BAE5AD2508DF0780x721B2492// SetInstancePriorityMode
void SET_INSTANCE_PRIORITY_MODE(int toggle);Parameters:toggle: toggles the instance priority modeSets the maximum prop density and changes a loading screen flag from 'loading story mode' to 'loading GTA Online'. It causes a loading screen to show as it reloads map data.Old name:  _ENABLE_MP_DLC_MAPSOld name:  _USE_FREEMODE_MAP_BEHAVIOROld name:  _LOWER_MAP_PROP_DENSITY
